(2, 'en', 'Help', 'help', NULL, '<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>Please read our FAQ before sending us a message.</p>\r\n<p><strong>FOR CUSTOMER :</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>How to Book at Porttie?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Find &amp; Explore</strong>&nbsp;&ndash;What are you searching for? Start your search below, and don\'t forget, it\'s free to place a listing for sale with us!.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Select</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; View the details of airport facilities, information and pricing facilities by pressing the &ldquo;get access&rdquo; button in the facility of your choice, then select the date and time of departure or arrival, flight code, and enter guest data for the verification process. Each facility has different inputs</li>\r\n<li><strong>order</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Click &ldquo;Book Now&rdquo; then your order will be added in Shopping Cart and you can add several different airport facilities in one same order.</li>\r\n<li><strong>View Cart</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; You can review your order before the payment process at the top right corner of Porttie website</li>\r\n<li><strong>Pay</strong>&nbsp;&ndash; Click &ldquo;Proceed To Checkout&rdquo; button in Cart menu and complete billing detail then click &ldquo;Place Order&rdquo; button to start payment process</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>I ordered service. What next?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You will receive a unique confirmation ticket via e-mail.</li>\r\n<li>Tickets must be checked before using our service.</li>\r\n<li>Please find the lounge you have ordered or search for pickup points upon arrival to start using our services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>How do you change the order date?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\">Please contact us from your account page</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span lang=\"en\" tabindex=\"0\"><strong>Which payment methods can be accepted?</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<pre id=\"tw-target-text\" class=\"tw-data-text tw-text-large tw-ta\" dir=\"ltr\" data-placeholder=\"Terjemahan\">Visa &amp; Mastercard credit cards, Mandiri clickpay, transfer and virtual accounts</pre>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS', 'FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS', 'FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-11-26 23:20:07', '2019-12-18 22:59:49', NULL),
(3, 'en', 'About Us', 'about', NULL, '<p><strong>WHAT IS PORTTIE?</strong></p>\r\n<p>Porttie is an online Marketplace specifically for booking Port Facilities (Land - Sea - Air). Like the online marketplace service sites provide rental facilities or purchase facilities from service providers to consumers. Anyone can promote their port facility services in Porttie and serve customers from all over the world for individual or group transactions.</p>\r\n<p>With the porttie guests can plan their trip comfortably and safely. We facilitate consumers to order directly from service providers through the website <a href=\"http://www.porttie.com\">www.porttie.com</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>WHO IS A PARTNER PORTTIE?</strong></p>\r\n<p>We collaborate with port companies (airports, seaports, land terminals) throughout Indonesia and collaborate with paid service providers at ports (land-sea-air) such as Fast Track, Exclusive Lounge, baggage wrapping services, luggage storage services, airport helper , and many other service providers. We open up opportunities for port service providers (Land-Sea-Air) that have not yet joined to register their facilities</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Join Porttie?</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Save time and let your customers choose their own service.</strong><br />why waste time explaining prices and service facilities for your customers while they can easily do it themselves.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Promote your service facilities</strong><br />As a partner, you can add and promote for free your facility services to Porttie users</p>\r\n<p><strong>Get customers easily from us</strong><br />When your customers start using Porttie, you will also immediately appear in our partner list and get customers from us</p>\r\n<p><strong>Only accept orders / valid reservations</strong><br />We require everyone to confirm their personal data, no. telephone and their email address before you receive their order and they will make payments directly on the Porttie website.</p>', NULL, 'About Marketplace specifically for booking Port Facilities', 'Porttie is an online Marketplace specifically for booking Port Facilities (Land - Sea - Air). Like the online marketplace service sites provide rental facilities or purchase facilities from service providers to consumers.', 'porttie, marketplace, airport service', 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-11-26 23:20:07', '2019-12-08 18:54:23', NULL),
(4, 'en', 'Terms and conditions', 'terms-and-conditions', NULL, '<h2 class=\"uppercase\">Term And&nbsp;Conditions</h2>\r\n<p>ePorttie, (&ldquo;we&rdquo; , &ldquo;us&rdquo; or &ldquo;our&rdquo;) provides Porttie services to Customers ( &ldquo; you&rdquo; or &ldquo;your &rdquo; ) either by itself or through its suppliers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Any voucher and all other documents and coupons issued in respect of Porttie services are furnished and issued subject to these Conditions of Contract and to any and all terms and conditions of the owners, operators, public carriers and such other persons who provide Porttie services to you. Copies of such terms and conditions are available on request. The purchase of Porttie services shall be deemed to constitute your consent and acceptance of these Conditions of Contract.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Definitions</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>In these Conditions of Contract: &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>(a) &ldquo;Booking Form&rdquo; means Porttie services Booking Form which is used by walk-in Customers.</p>\r\n<p>(b) &ldquo;call centre&rdquo; means Porttie services call centre on (+62) 361 755 136.</p>\r\n<p>(c) &ldquo;Conditions of Contract&rdquo; means these conditions of contract as amended by us from time to time.</p>\r\n<p>(d) &ldquo;Customer(s)&rdquo; means any person booking Porttie services and/or covered by that booking.</p>\r\n<p>(e) &ldquo;Porttie services&rdquo; means all and any of the services and products provided by us as described on the Website from time to time.</p>\r\n<p>(f) &ldquo;No Show&rdquo; means the failure by any Customer for whom Porttie services have been booked to utilize those Porttie services.</p>\r\n<p>(g) &ldquo;Website&rdquo; means Porttie services website at www.thebaliconcierge.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n<li>Booking Porttie services</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>2.1 We will provide Porttie services to you and any other person covered by your booking on arrival at, or departure from,